{"tid":1722642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[如果你係個有包袱嘅冷氣軍師]有一批人捱緊餓需要你幫","createTime":"2019-11-15T03:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T03:14:46.000Z","uid":274292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f741c9934a4dff3f673e20d5d4e47aed036bc05","tid":1722642,"uid":274292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"嗰批人就係獨居長者，有好多社福機構送唔到飯，但我地手頭冇佢地地址，或者要大家行下自己大廈，睇下有冇人係留在係屋企走唔到，佢地多數真係自力更生唔到，被社會遺棄，屋企人又唔要，有機會已經兩日冇食過野。<br />\n<br />\n唔駛當主任去做，當閑任去做，最好係聯絡當區議員一齊做。你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有社福機構會作為主辦，招收當區可以幫手嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過點突破同溫層，如果做得成，有冇人比我地更貼近基層。雖然好似用左黎做政治，但我地真係本住良心做，偉大嘅連登仔們請施以援手。<br />\n<br />\n你地話好唔好?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">光復香港，<br />\n時代革命。</span></span>"},{"pid":"268511e187e97e728767b295ae82f25ef80dd7e6","tid":1722642,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"送飯送到要過海？"},{"pid":"7cd29458530377b966b3483a8781f08fe7d7ea78","tid":1722642,"uid":274292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"268511e187e97e728767b295ae82f25ef80dd7e6","tid":1722642,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"送飯送到要過海？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:04:45.000Z","msg":"唔駛，比你都唔會去喇"},{"pid":"8397eabda41b4ef3a30b83c186667ad32744e2c5","tid":1722642,"uid":274292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9e87093465238663a21b1e90f7741f2a9b21a58","tid":1722642,"uid":274292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:14:46.000Z","msg":"推"}]}